              </div>
              <div class="tableWrap">
                <table>
                  <thead><tr><th>Booking</th><th>Trip</th><th>Customer</th><th>Seat</th><th>Status</th><th>Total</th><th></th></tr></thead>
                  <tbody id="recentBookings"></tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="cardHead">
                <div class="cardTitle"><h3>Quick actions</h3><p>Fast company management actions.</p></div>
              </div>
              <div class="cardPad">
                <div class="quickGrid">
                  <button class="quickCard" data-modal="create" data-type="vehicle"><div class="quickIcon"><i class="fa-solid fa-bus-simple"></i></div><strong>Create vehicle</strong><span>Create a coach, shuttle, ferry, train, or flight seat layout.</span></button>
                  <button class="quickCard" data-modal="create" data-type="listing"><div class="quickIcon"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i></div><strong>Create listing</strong><span>Add the service customers will discover and book.</span></button>
                  <button class="quickCard" data-modal="create" data-type="departure"><div class="quickIcon"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-plus"></i></div><strong>Create departure</strong><span>Select route and vehicle, then create trip inventory.</span></button>
                  <button class="quickCard" data-modal="create" data-type="route"><div class="quickIcon"><i class="fa-solid fa-route"></i></div><strong>Create route</strong><span>Link stops to an existing transport listing.</span></button>
                  <button class="quickCard" data-modal="create" data-type="check-in"><div class="quickIcon"><i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode"></i></div><strong>Check in ticket</strong><span>Validate a ticket and release earnings after service starts.</span></button>
                  <button class="quickCard" data-modal="edit" data-type="seat map"><div class="quickIcon"><i class="fa-solid fa-chair"></i></div><strong>Edit seats</strong><span>Update seat map, blocked seats, or room stock.</span></button>
                  <button class="quickCard" data-modal="create" data-type="promotion"><div class="quickIcon"><i class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></i></div><strong>Boost listing</strong><span>Promote your service at the top of searches.</span></button>
                  <button class="quickCard" data-jump="billing"><div class="quickIcon"><i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i></div><strong>Upgrade plan</strong><span>Open billing, select a plan, and continue to payment.</span></button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section" id="listings">
          <div class="card" data-tabs>
            <div class="cardHead">
